com.nastenkapusechka.validation.annotaions

Annotation Type PhoneNumber


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
public @interface PhoneNumber
    The annotation checks the validity of the number in the international format. The number must be represented by a string

    If you want to hang annotation on the map, you must definitely specify the target for verification (keys or values)
